{"tid":1520183,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"四年前既<<十年>>而家一一應驗","createTime":"2019-08-30T17:19:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T17:29:29.000Z","uid":56230,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bd8013c260c511aa709337e890071ad101f4164c","tid":1520183,"uid":56230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T17:19:59.000Z","msg":"先講浮瓜 電影入面政府同西環聯手自編自導自演槍擊案 目的就係製造社會恐慌 強推國安法<br />\n就好似777縱容暴力 加埋cctvb既助攻 近幾日仲漏下口風 試下市民對緊急法反應<br />\n再加上剛剛既斬警事件 到底係自編自導自演定點 不作評論 但敢肯定既係 不論示威者定黑警 都已提升雙方既暴力程度 政府只要往後製造輿論 就可以達到造成社會恐慌既結果<br />\n<br />\n再講方言 而家d小學生已經浮係講普通話 過多10年8年等班仔出黎做野 相信同故事入面一樣 唔識普通話 食蕉都無得做<br />\n<br />\n再黎係本地蛋 雖然香港而家未有紅衛兵 但近呢2個月 藍絲督灰風氣盛行 幾多手足因為比人督而搞到周身蟻<br />\n過多十年八年 可能講寵物小精靈唔係乜柒布可夢都比人掟雞蛋<br />\n<br />\n跟住係自焚者 呢2個月 死左幾多義士都唔使講啦<br />\n<br />\n最後係冬蟬 我諗香港人未到2047都可以拎黎做標本了"},{"pid":"bfe756fd12aba2d620acd4207e863cf12fcfb4fb","tid":1520183,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T17:20:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dyrx7H5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDyrx7H5.gif&h=f7c0f28c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2c%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=b04e6475\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2c%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=d94e31d9\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2c%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=2e4edc1c\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"0c25482afb6236aa7a30bfed66bc0ce57d566d93","ti